{
"#name"
:
{
"llmf"
:
null
,
"cn"
:
"基于 llamafile 零依赖运行本地大语言模型"
,
"en"
:
"Zero-dependency local LLM runner based on llamafile"
}
,
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"基于 llamafile 运行本地大语言模型，无需依赖、无需配置。\n\n主要功能：\n- 启动本地 API 服务器 (serve)，支持 OpenAI 兼容接口\n- 命令行对话模式 (cli)，快速生成文本\n- 交互式聊天 (chat)，支持多轮对话\n- 模型管理 (model)，支持下载/导入/导出/查询\n- 文本分词 (tokenize)，分析文本 token 数量\n\n支持模型格式：GGUF、llamafile\n"
,
"en"
:
"Run local large language models based on llamafile, zero dependencies, zero configuration.\n\nKey features:\n- Start local API server (serve) with OpenAI-compatible interface\n- CLI mode (cli) for quick text generation\n- Interactive chat (chat) with multi-turn conversation\n- Model management (model) with download/import/export/query\n- Text tokenization (tokenize) to analyze token count\n\nSupported formats: GGUF, llamafile\n"
}
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"使用提示：\n1. 首次使用运行 'x llmf init' 进行交互式配置\n2. 使用 'x llmf serve --nobrowser' 启动 API 服务\n3. 在终端用 '@l' 快捷指令进行聊天\n4. 模型存储在 ~/.x-cmd/data/llmf/model/ 目录\n"
,
"en"
:
"Usage tips:\n1. Run 'x llmf init' for interactive first-time setup\n2. Use 'x llmf serve --nobrowser' to start API service\n3. Use '@l' shortcut in terminal for chat\n4. Models are stored in ~/.x-cmd/data/llmf/model/\n"
}
]
,
"#synopsis"
:
[
{
"x llmf <subcmd> [options] [args]"
:
null
}
,
{
"x llmf serve -m <model> [--port <port>] [--host <host>]"
:
null
}
,
{
"x llmf cli -p '<prompt>' [-m <model>] [--temp <temp>]"
:
null
}
,
{
"x llmf model <action> [model_name]"
:
null
}
]
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x llmf init"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 交互式初始化配置"
,
"en"
:
"Example: interactive initialization"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x llmf serve -m llava/v1.5-7b/q4_k.gguf --nobrowser"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 启动 API 服务"
,
"en"
:
"Example: start API server"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x llmf cli -p 'Write a Python function'"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 命令行快速生成文本"
,
"en"
:
"Example: quick text generation"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x llmf model ls"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 列出本地模型"
,
"en"
:
"Example: list local models"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x llmf model download llava/v1.5-7b/q4_k.gguf"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 下载指定模型"
,
"en"
:
"Example: download specific model"
}
]
,
"#subcmd:Server"
:
[
"serve"
,
"tokenize"
]
,
"#subcmd:Interface"
:
[
"cli"
,
"chat"
]
,
"#subcmd:Model"
:
[
"model"
]
,
"#subcmd:Config"
:
[
"init"
,
"--cfg"
,
"--cur"
]
,
"serve"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"启动 API 服务器模式，提供 OpenAI 兼容的 HTTP 接口"
,
"en"
:
"Start API server mode with OpenAI-compatible HTTP interface"
}
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x llmf serve -m llava/v1.5-7b/q4_k.gguf --nobrowser"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 启动 API 服务"
,
"en"
:
"Example: start API server"
}
]
